'''珍妮佛·傑森·李'''（{{lang-en|'''Jennifer Jason Leigh'''}}，{{bd|1962年|2月5日}}）是一位美國女演員、導演、監製和編劇。較著名的作品如《[[布魯克林黑街|布魯克林黑街]]》（1989年）、《[[邁阿密特別行動|邁阿密特別行動]]》（1990年）、《[[浴火赤子情|浴火赤子情]]》（1991年）、《[[派克夫人的情人|派克夫人的情人]]》（1994年）、《[[珍愛姐妹情|珍愛姐妹情]]》（2007年）和《[[八惡人|八惡人]]》（2015年）。其中，因《八惡人》而提名了[[奧斯卡最佳女配角獎|奧斯卡最佳女配角獎]]和[[金球獎最佳電影女配角|金球獎最佳電影女配角]]。2001年，她與[[艾倫·康明|艾倫·康明]]共同執導、監製和編劇了《[[真愛大吐槽|真愛大吐槽]]》。

== 早期生活 ==
李出生於[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]，父親[[維克·莫羅|維克·莫羅]]是一名演員，而母親[[芭芭拉·透納|芭芭拉·透納]]則是名編劇和前演員<ref name=avclub>{{cite web|url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/jennifer-jason-leigh,14179/|title=Interview: Jennifer Jason Leigh|last=Tobias|first=Scott|work=The Onion A.V. Club|accessdate=2013-03-21|archive-date=2013-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624194658/http://www.avclub.com/articles/jennifer-jason-leigh,14179/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=guardian_interview>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2005/mar/12/features.weekend|title=What you see and what you get|last=Williams|first=Zoe|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|location=London|date=2005-03-12|accessdate=2013-03-21}}</ref>。父母後來離了婚<ref name=tca>Stated on ''[[Inside_the_Actors_Studio|Inside the Actors Studio]]'', 1999</ref>。繼父是導演<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.kveller.com/jewish-actress-jennifer-jason-leigh-on-being-a-mom-actress/|title=Jewish Actress Jennifer Jason Leigh on Being a Mom & Actress|author=|last=Valente|first=Joanna C.|date=February 23, 2016|work=|newspaper=Kveller|accessdate=June 4, 2018|language=|archive-date=2018-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714221930/https://www.kveller.com/jewish-actress-jennifer-jason-leigh-on-being-a-mom-actress/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的出生名為「珍妮佛·李·莫羅」，在演藝生涯的早期改掉，將自己的中間取自她家庭的朋友[[傑森·羅巴茲|傑森·羅巴茲]]。李的父母是[[猶太人|猶太人]]，分別來自[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]和[[奧地利|奧地利]]的[[猶太|猶太]]家庭<ref name=wea>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.ca/newspapers?id=ZCcdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=T6UEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6758,5552267&dq=actor-eulogized-for-finest-performance&hl=en|title=Actor Eulogized For Finest Performance|publisher=[[The_Tuscaloosa_News|The Tuscaloosa News]]|page=20|date=1982-07-27|accessdate=2010-11-23|archive-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312143631/https://news.google.ca/newspapers?id=ZCcdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=T6UEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6758,5552267&dq=actor-eulogized-for-finest-performance&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=sweyr>{{cite news|title=Age: A State of Mind|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&s_site=mercurynews&p_multi=SJ&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB719E9E284E90A&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|publisher=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|date=1992-08-10|accessdate=2010-11-23|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024011644/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&s_site=mercurynews&p_multi=SJ&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB719E9E284E90A&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ubi">{{cite book|title=Fade to Black: A Book of Movie Obituaries|url=https://archive.org/details/fadetoblackbooko0000donn_b4o0|last=Donnelley|first=Paul|publisher=Omnibus|year=2003|page=[https://archive.org/details/fadetoblackbooko0000donn_b4o0/page/504 504]|isbn=0-7119-9512-5}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000492/bio |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127082509/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000492/bio |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jta.org/2016/02/26/life-religion/5-incredible-jewish-stories-behind-this-years-oscars|title=5 incredible Jewish stories behind this year’s Oscars|last=Friedman|first=Gabe|date=February 26, 2016|website=JTA - Jewish news|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522041840/https://www.jta.org/2016/02/26/life-religion/5-incredible-jewish-stories-behind-this-years-oscars|archive-date=2018-05-22|dead-url=no|access-date=May 21, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amctheatres.com/movies/good-time-53848|quote=Her father was of Russian Jewish descent and her mother was of Austrian Jewish ancestry.|work=AMC Theatres|title=Good Time|date=August 11, 2017|access-date=May 21, 2018|archive-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404101601/https://www.amctheatres.com/movies/good-time-53848|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她有一個姊姊嘉莉·安·莫羅（Carrie Ann Morrow），她曾擔任1995年電影《[[落翅天使|落翅天使]]》的技術顧問。此外，還有一個同父異母妹妹米娜·巴迪（Mina Badie），曾和她一起參演過2001年電影《[[真愛大吐槽|真愛大吐槽]]》。

